          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/03/25750596/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_3817162551003777747.png",
                "id": "talent20504",
                "key": "Seal of Approval",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Seal of Approval"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 3 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span>. Karakter ini memperoleh status <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Scarlet Seal</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Scarlet Seal</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Saat Karakter melancarkan Charged Attack:</span> Mengakibatkan DMG +2.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 1 </span>(Dapat ditumpuk hingga 2 lapis)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/03/25750596/5bef20ac953cae4a26b35ba84c55c406_626447552697778161.png",
                "id": "talent42563",
                "key": "Signed Edict",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Signed Edict"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 3 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span>. Karakter ini memperoleh status <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Scarlet Seal</span> dan <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Brilliance</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Scarlet Seal</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Saat Karakter melancarkan Charged Attack:</span> Mengakibatkan DMG +2. </p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 1</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Brilliance</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Saat Karakter melancarkan Charged Attack: </span>Mengonsumsi 1 <span style=\"color: #FF9999\">Pyro</span> lebih sedikit. (Sekali setiap Ronde) </p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Tahap Selesai:</span> Karakter memperoleh status <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Scarlet Seal</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Durasi (Ronde): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/03/25750596/2c415dc76ad1e6437d2144d4c998f35b_2673741695354349847.png",
                "id": "talent23731",
                "key": "Done Deal",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Done Deal"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Pyro dan dapat memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini, target berganti ke Karakter selanjutnya secara paksa</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, menciptakan [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] yang mengakibatkan 1 poin Pyro DMG di akhir Ronde (Jumlah penggunaan sekali, maksimum 2 tumpukan)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/03/25750596/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_1815071503911497626.png",
                "id": "talent5462",
                "key": "Pyro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Pyro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Charged Attack</span></strong></p><p>Jika total Dadu Elemental berjumlah genap sebelum Aksi Tempur giliranmu dimulai, maka Normal Attack yang digunakan akan dianggap sebagai Charged Attack.<br><br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/03/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_8767167326600714525.png",
